{"tid":1661876,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[裝備圖鑑]3M HF-802","createTime":"2019-10-18T11:30:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-27T16:32:18.000Z","uid":81243,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"6493ea4f7f26d523bc56ba757d5032b42ad39d2a","tid":1661876,"uid":81243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T11:30:59.000Z","msg":"喺工友仍然連60926都唔識上嘅時候,3M就出咗隻新半罩HF-801/2/3同有Speaking Diaphragm(唔識譯)嘅HF-801/2/3SD,務求令各位工友喺PPE市場入面患上選擇困難症。<br />\n<br />\n有見及此,一名工友聯絡本人後,慷慨露出咗自己嘅HF-802,以便各位工友選擇適合自己嘅PPE<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zjAbjdm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzjAbjdm.jpg&h=76904463&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n包裝<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iZ5q8aj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiZ5q8aj.jpg&h=86d1b299&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nD8094 ABEK1P3(比60926勁少少)<br />\n聲明:工友並沒有收取任何廣告費,圖中某品牌汽水罐只作比例之用<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/U1t4Egc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FU1t4Egc.jpg&h=8df32046&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n半罩本體(戴嘅方法同其他半罩一樣)<br />\n可以見到有三粒藍色掣,撳實中間嘅掣可以鎖死進氣(做Seal Check)<br />\n左右兩邊用嚟拆Filter<br />\n聲明同上<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F5zLoLi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF5zLoLi.jpg&h=3352a060&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呼氣閥<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iz0Omxf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fiz0Omxf.jpg&h=dfe1420f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n內部,可見HF-802進氣閥(中間)比其他半罩大<br />\n上方圓形空洞喺保留俾Speaking Diaphragm(HF-802SD用),HF-802因為冇Speaking Diaphragm所以封咗<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bzdTxFx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbzdTxFx.jpg&h=6c3629eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n濾罐卡位,有防呆設計,不過工友同我對能否阻止香港人上錯Filter有保留<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nQ&amp;A<br />\n<br />\nQ:想買<br />\nA:去RS HK<br />\n<a href=\"https://hkcn.rs-online.com/mobile/p/reusable-respirators/1901912/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkcn.rs-online.com%2Fmobile%2Fp%2Freusable-respirators%2F1901912%2F&d=JQdTOMZ4NvWA5L1F4kLiz%2BrBpkLuHOqafswNxXmn3gI%3D&h=24870f88\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hkcn.rs-online.com/mobile/p/reusable-respirators/1901912/</a><br />\nHF-802<br />\n<a href=\"https://hkcn.rs-online.com/mobile/p/reusable-respirators/1901913/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkcn.rs-online.com%2Fmobile%2Fp%2Freusable-respirators%2F1901913%2F&d=JQdTOMZ4NvWA5L1F4kLiz%2BrBpkLuHOqafswNxXmn3gI%3D&h=a0b61679\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hkcn.rs-online.com/mobile/p/reusable-respirators/1901913/</a><br />\nHF-802SD（冇貨)<br />\n<br />\nQ:點揀Filter?<br />\nA:出門右轉FB無名博士<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n工友用後感<br />\n<br />\n由於最近工程甚少,所以缺乏用後報告<br />\nFilter兩邊入氣,二二如四,一對四個入氣口(明點解進氣閥咁大啦？)<br />\n材質雖然係矽膠,不過比6502QL/7502硬,但仍然舒服<br />\n上嘅方法同其他3M半罩一樣<br />\n整體唔重,輕過6502QL+60926<br />\nFilter要大大力上,一定要聽到Click一聲（期待地下一埋免費Filter)<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">由於Filter比正常6092X貴,而且香港並不普及,因此有以下風險:冇備用Filter冇人幫你、俾Madam點相、俾人話係鬼</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n同行敬請安全至上，最後敬祝武運昌隆"},{"pid":"9968f5ade970264e74c108e0ff8a1f1f4e4c015b","tid":1661876,"uid":81243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T11:31:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"67101c12c62ca59ed71fff594cfc7a474bb5a12a","tid":1661876,"uid":81243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T11:31:24.000Z","msg":"再推"},{"pid":"2a5ab4046373a1d5287d5eddd194b3987f00714e","tid":1661876,"uid":81243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T11:31:36.000Z","msg":"三"},{"pid":"f045814d897bb9c156a6a810541d6f838736a6ea","tid":1661876,"uid":81243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T11:31:47.000Z","msg":"4/10"},{"pid":"5ad3cc42d51d198001bbee0a6285d7b54f0693c6","tid":1661876,"uid":81243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"repl